The Nigeria Labour Congress (NLC) has Commiserate with the government and people of Borno state over the demise of the former governor of the state, Alhaji Mohammed Goni NLC in a condolence message addressed to governor of the state, prof Babagana Zulum described the late Goni as an elder statesman and a fine gentleman. The message which was signed by NLC President, Comrade Ayuba Wabba said as former governor of old Borno state under the GNPP, Mohammed Goni was instrumental to several developmental projects some of which still endure in the state. Wabba said the late former governor will be missed by the people of Borno state and the broader spectrum of the Nigerian society.